724
00:59:17,560 --> 00:59:22,280
counterfactuals: Is the opposite true? 
Would this be better if I did it a year  

725
00:59:22,280 --> 00:59:28,440
ago or a year from now? What does a smart coach 
conclude given the same information without you  

726
00:59:28,440 --> 00:59:34,080
sharing your conclusion? So there's a lot of 
techniques for, how well can you test this?  

727
00:59:34,080 --> 00:59:37,920
What would convince you if you were wrong? 
This is kind of deep canvassing yourself.

