00:59:43,440 --> 00:59:46,720
applied these tactics, if there's 
a story there of something that's  

730
00:59:46,720 --> 00:59:50,880
emerged out of a company you've 
worked with thinking this way.

731
00:59:50,880 --> 00:59:55,160
I will tell you, I've worked with four startups 
